      "highlights" : "Increase in danger of wet avalanches in the course of the day.",
      "comment" : "As a consequence of warming during the day and solar radiation there will be an increase in the danger of wet avalanches. In particular at the base of rock walls avalanches can be released naturally. <br/> Individual avalanche prone locations for dry avalanches are to be found on very steep shady slopes above approximately 2500 m. Such avalanche prone locations are difficult to recognise. <br/> The danger of ground avalanches will increase during the day."
